OL,3,CDeath of the gearbox? Automatic
OL,4,Cdriving tests skyrocket
OL,6,FMost instructors are still teaching
OL,7,Flearners in manual cars, AA Driving
OL,8,FSchool data suggests, but the number
OL,9,Fof people learning in automatics is on
OL,10,Fthe rise.
OL,12,FIn January 2022 86% of instructors
OL,13,Fwere teaching in manual cars, and that
OL,14,Fnumber had dropped to 81% by July 2023.
OL,16,FOverall, in 2023, 37% of people
OL,17,Ftraining to be a driving instructor
OL,18,Fwith the AA chose an automatic vehicle.
